Technology Brief -- Cirrus Logic Inc.:
   Firm Reaches Pact to Buy
   Closely Held Chip Maker
Acumos sells chips that control the displays in desktop
personal computers, complementing Cirrus's strength in
control chips for lap-top and notebook PCs, Cirrus said.
Under the agreement, Acumos's products and employees will be
merged into Cirrus. Doug Bartek, president and chief
executive of Acumos, will become a Cirrus vice president,
Cirrus said.